  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT324-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">ceṟippaṟivuṟukkappaṭṭu “irā vārā varaival” eṉṟāṟkut tōḻi atu maṟuttu
          varaivu kaṭāyatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">The confidante inquiring about marriage, refusing that
          (atu?) to him who said “I will marry without coming at night”, after he was informed of
          [her] confinement. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT324">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> koṭuṅkāṉ mutalaik kōḷva lēṟṟai</l>
          <l> vaḻivaḻak kaṟukkuṅ kāṉalam peruntuṟai</l>
          <l> yiṉamī ṉiruṅkaḻi nīnti nīniṉ</l>
          <l> ṉayaṉuṭai maiyiṉ varuti yivaṭaṉ</l>
          <l> maṭaṉuṭai maiyi ṉuyaṅkum yāṉatu</l>
          <l> kavaimaka nañcuṇ ṭāaṅ</l>
          <l> kañcuval perumaveṉ ṉeñcat tāṉē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l rend="indent">By the big ghat of the seashore grove,</l>
          <l rend="indent3">where the murderous, strong male of the bent-legged crocodile</l>
          <l rend="indent3">tears apart what wanders on the way ,</l>
          <l>you swim the dark backwaters with fishes in swarms</l>
          <l>[and] come, possessed by longing.</l>
          <l rend="indent">While she, possessed by her inexperience, is weakened –</l>
          <l rend="indent2">as if my twin children had eaten poison,</l>
          <l>I am afraid, o great one, in my heart.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
